 er en del av Statnetts driftskontrollsystem som best\u00e5r i dag av en landssentral, tre regionsentraler samt lokalkontroll i Statnetts stasjoner. Regionsentralene vil fra 1. september 2016 ligge i Alta og Oslo."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|moreromsdal"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4fb7deaa9dc9f67ae5a35be873e4e1edb30e9adbb4c3a7a09a75b8b698ec819f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T07:59:08.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Et enstemmig Statnett-styre har vedtatt \u00e5 flytte regionsentralen for Midt-Norge til Alta."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9410859.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/statnett%20adressa%203.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7654379177fa1ffc6806be4b6f9230ae5d930237.jpg?5959ffb0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Statnett legger ned p\u00e5 Sunndals\u00f8ra -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7654379177fa1ffc6806be4b6f9230ae5d930237"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "moreromsdal"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "regionsentralen"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["alta og oslo", "statnett", "sundnals\u00f8ra"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["sunndals\u00f8ra", "midt-norge", "alta"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["\u00f8ivind rue", "ivar bullv\u00e5g hansen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/moreromsdal"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9410859.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/statnet